name: NSColorSpace.Model
desc: Constants that describe the abstract model on which color space objects are based.

items.name: case lab
items.desc: The L*a*b* device-independent color-space model, which represents colors relative to a reference white point.

items.name: case deviceN
items.desc: The DeviceN color-space model from Adobe Systems, Inc.

items.name: case indexed
items.desc: An indexed color space, which identifies discrete colors in a color list by index number.

items.name: case patterned
items.desc: A pattern color space, which is a repeated image that creates a tiled pattern.
